These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, house, punk
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | house | electronic | gospel | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, pony, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | goldfish | pony | goat | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, singing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | singing | traveling | magic-tricks | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, tram, car
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | tram | boat | quad-bike | car |

 #################################

 
